data.description: Super cute 4 bed 2 bath home with all the modern finishes & a fantastic fenced backyard with a shed & awesome deck. This multi-level has 3 bedrooms all on one level, 4th bedroom in the lower level with great living room space & newer carpet. Large attached heated garage with cabinets great for entertaining! This one is close to the park and the elementary school so check it out soon!
